Given a non-negative integer N. The task is to check if N is a power of 2. More formally, 
check if N can be expressed as 2x for some integer x. Return true if N is power of 2 else return false.
CODE:
def isPowerOfTwo(n):
    if (n == 0):
        return False
    while (n != 1):
        if (n % 2 != 0):
            return False
        n = n // 2
 
    return True
